with tabs as (select stock_code, ("days"-"ordered"::float)/"ordered" as "val", "quantity" from
(select stock_code, extract(days from "recent"-"early" + interval '1d') as "days", "ordered", "quantity"
from
(select
  stock_code,
  max(invoice_date) as "recent",
  min(invoice_date) as "early",
  count(distinct date_trunc('day', invoice_date)) as "ordered",
  sum(quantity) as "quantity"
from (select * from country_data('$region', '$month') where invoice_num not like 'C%') as ord
group by stock_code) as t1) as t2) 
select stock_code as "Stock Code"  from tabs
where val>0 and quantity>'$min_qty'
order by  val desc, quantity desc
